# UL_PINREF

## Data members

| | |
| --- | --- |
| instance | UL_INSTANCE |
| part | UL_PART |
| pin | UL_PIN |

See also UL_SEGMENT, UL_CONTACTREF

## Example

```
schematic(SCH) {
 SCH.sheets(SH) {
 printf("Sheet: %d\n", SH.number);
 SH.nets(N) {
 printf("\tNet: %s\n", N.name);
 N.segments(SEG) {
 SEG.pinrefs(P) {
 printf("connected to: %s, %s, %s\n",
 P.part.name, P.instance.name, P.pin.name);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 }
```





